RPG PM Portfolio Website

Overview

A single-page React + TypeScript application showcasing PM skills through an RPG character interface. The page features a side-by-side layout with a character picker on one side and skills charts on the other.

Technology Stack





React 18 with TypeScript for type safety



Vite for fast development and building



Recharts for spider charts (soft skills) and horizontal bar charts (hard skills)



Framer Motion for smooth animations



CSS Modules or Tailwind CSS for styling (dark theme)



React Icons for UI elements

